17 §3125.1. Accreditation; powers of the Board of Regents
18 The Board of Regents shall have the power to set policy regarding the
19 accreditation of all public postsecondary institutions, as provided in Chapter
20 25-B of Title 17 of the Louisiana Revised Statutes of 1950.
